Kumagai cites progress on spinoff plan . Kumagai Gumi ( Hong Kong ) Ltd has won preliminary approval from the Stock Exchange of Hong Kong ' s listing committee to list its China infrastructure unit , the South China Morning Post said on Friday , quoting chairman Yu Ching - po . Yu was quoted as saying the timing wuld depend on further developments in Yangpu industrial zone , Hainan province , where the infrastructure project is located , and market conditions . Company officials were not immediately available for comment . - - Hong Kong Newsroom ( 852 ) 2843 6441 
